name: Samsung Multi-Codec Blu-ray and DVD Player
description: Support for the largest number of codec and file formats means you can access and enjoy a wider range of video, image and audio content than ever before. Many popular video formats such as Flash and QuickTime are supported, as well as VOB files from DVDs. In addition to MP3 audio, you can listen to lossless FLAC files as well as .WMA, .OGG, .WAV and more. Pictures can be viewed in the popular JPEG picture format, as well as PNG files, GIF files and more.
